item.title: TN-33 South at US-25E
item.description: TN-33 South at US-25E in Claiborne County. Turn right for US-25E North/TN-33 South to Tazewell; left for US-25E South to Morristown.

item.title: US-25E South at TN-33
item.description: US-25E South at TN-33 in Tazewell. Turn left for US-25E South/TN-33 North to Morristown. Continue straight for TN-33 South to Maynardville.

item.title: US-25E South at TNS-345

item.title: US-25E South Approaching TN-33
item.description: US-25E South Approaching TN-33 in Tazewell. Use left lane to continue south on US-25E/To I-81.

item.title: US-25E South - Welcome To Tennessee
item.description: Welcome to Tennessee on US-25 South. Taken just south of the Cumberland Gap tunnel.

item.title: US-25E South at US-58 Interchange

item.title: End US-58 West at US-25E

item.title: US-58 West Approaching US-25E
